This paper deals with the generation of private keys in a network, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The network involves communication between multiple terminals, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of fading channels in a wireless network, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and signal processing (cs.SI).
